==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Constructionist
<hw>Con*struc"tion*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who puts a certain
construction upon some writing or instrument, as the Constitutions of
the United States; <as>as, a strict <ex>constructionist</ex>; a broad
<ex>constructionist</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Constructive</ent>⟦br⟧
